Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:25.09,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:55.18,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:53.78,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:01.50,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you proceed now that things have taken a turn for the worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe in fortune telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fate that awaits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a storybook vision of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you leave me behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Heaven, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuckin' bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You followed me here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Namatame Taro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the ones I saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This dude high or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to save this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Nanako back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You put the people you saw on the Midnight Channel into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,On rainy nights... on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,they signal me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to save them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Signal you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't put you in the TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,how would you have ended up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say that we wouldn't have been able to face ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But we nearly died!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's completely lost it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you! "Save," my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just killing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you plan on killing this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a {\i1}savior!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,H-His power is attracting more and more Shadows to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, I'm going to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rash, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I will... I will save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My body...{is moving on its own!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?{SAY IT SAY IT SAY IT}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, run!{I MIGHT START RAPING YOU.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is controlling him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Who knew this guy would be such a pain in the ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's charging up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so he can take us out in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I won't let anyone get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!{oh hey, it stopped.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, don't fight with them.{BY THE POWER OF LOLI I COMMAND YOU}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shi—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is...{MOVING ON ITS OWN, RIGHT????}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...moving...{SAY IT. SAY IT.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...on its own!{FUCK YEA!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to save that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, please save Nanako!{AHHHH GHOST HAND}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohryu?!{ultimate hierophant persona? omg}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can move again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done enough!{they're making naoto's persona seem useful}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Shadows are going bear-serk!{Oh, shout out to that one guy on /a/}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rawr!{Who is using that subtitle renderer that displays comments}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako? Nanako!{You really should get a better media player}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's must be in pain, but she doesn't seem to be injured anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This place must not be good for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to carry her out, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,still hasn't recovered from her cold.{... FUCKING JAPAN}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then to go through that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana's still so small,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so her other self didn't appear like it did for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And she got caught in all that craziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All those Shadows just had to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she could've handled that, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I waste time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,listening to what Namatame had to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't tried to engage him in conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd rescued Nanako immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto, it isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i}is{\i0} my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, I prioritized solving the case over Nanako's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, Nanako is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,enough of this pity party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is feeling pathetic and consoling each other gonna solve anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together, Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you desperately trying to save Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys. Acting all gloomy won't solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Think how Nanako would feel if she saw us like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, you were pretty cool for once, Kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, don't make a scene in the hospital. Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the fog especially thick today?{so's my dick}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it's really cold, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out. It's about Namatame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he regained consciousness this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"According to the police interrogation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he confessed that he regrets what he did and admits that he was just scared."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So he admitted to his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At long last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I received word from the hospital this morning that it's okay to visit Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should go see her when school lets out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like Nanako's doing a bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God.{CHRISTIAN PROPAGANDA}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, where's Naoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to invite her too, but she wasn't in her classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?{senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So Nanako's doing better?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just having a hard time believing that the case is truly over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You would.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're a unique person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You referred to me as your friend, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what you said at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm glad you were there."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted someone to acknowledge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was trying so desperately to solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take away my ability as a detective, I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said you were happy that I was there. {typo in stream}{thank you for leaving it in}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave me a place where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're headed for the schoolyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, weren't we going to see Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still just lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, y-you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. She isn't able to talk a lot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima, you came here again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you're worried about your daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but you still need your rest, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'll wheel him back to his room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing, Adachi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima, that's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,About Namatame...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still mentally unstable,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're slowly piecing together his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything new?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is still a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess it's okay to tell you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There were entries about Ms. Yamano and Ms. Konishi in the diary we found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Namatame had been making advances on Ms. Konishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We think that could be connected to why he killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I'm gonna go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bottle it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame's been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't hurt anyone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you think Nanako can go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima's still hospitalized, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wonder what's up with this fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a person whose child has been bedridden because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's really poisonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Evacuate immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is poisonous gas! It's loaded with viruses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die if you breathe this fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him? What a creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The idea that this fog is poisonous is just plain stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Although that was an extreme example,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that people are getting increasingly worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,People everywhere are talking about the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very unusual for fog to last this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Visibility's so bad, it's kinda scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean in the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Guys, put on your glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These glasses are meant to help us see through the fog in the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But putting that aside, no glasses would improve one's visibility in a fog under normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the fog from over there be leaking into our world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You guys think that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It just popped into my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the fog from the TV world really be leaking into our world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It does seem a lot like the fog on the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but beyond that, I'm clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the case against Namatame hasn't been going well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,they haven't made any progress with Namatame's interrogations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he's still confined to his hospital bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so further interrogation has yet to commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The fog isn't leaving, and the interrogation isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We solved the case, but I still feel bummed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I still stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What brought that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept your promise to help me find the person who was disrupting the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So I should be going back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't wanna go until Nana gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do we have to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe I should move in with you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Being together would really heat things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, it {\i1}has{\i0} been unusually cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you promised Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I promised that we'd go buy a space heater.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're getting a space heater, we'd better get some oranges to complete the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji, what'd you buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that wool?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Nanako and I could make some knitted animals when she gets better,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so they're for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji, you're so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're all here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't we pick out a Christmas present for Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The space heater isn't good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, as soon as Nanako's out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,how about we have a party at your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A party? That sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! And we'll bake the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1035)}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(741,1035)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1149,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(534,1035)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1360.5,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(429,1035)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1467,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310.5,1035)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1588.5,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(180,1035)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720.5,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(51,1036.5)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1852.5,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no you're not! Are you {\i1}trying{\i0} to send Nanako back to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is {dog}Narukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Keep calm and hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a sudden change in Nanako's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry over to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a family member?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.92,0:22:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big brother's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.15,0:22:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I even looked at some space heaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.87,0:23:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go buy one together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to make snowmen when it snows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.63,0:23:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised that we'd play together a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay with you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.20,0:23:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How come he's the one who gets to live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put an end to this ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.14,0:24:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We must... reach out to the truth.
